{"url": "https://people.com/country/cmt-awards-2018-dierks-bentley-daughter-jordan-walk-red-carpet/", "text": "It\u2019s bring-your-daughter-to-work day!\n\nDierks Bentley hit up the 2018 CMT Music Awards in Nashville Wednesday night and brought a very special guest: his 7-year-old daughter Jordan.\n\nThe country star, 42, and his middle child rocked matching outfits when they posed outside of Bridgestone Arena. Dad wore grey pants with a white tee, black denim jacket and distressed combat boots, while Jordan sported a graphic tee, black tulle skirt and black kitten heels.\n\nBentley is set to perform at the awards show, where he\u2019ll hit the stage with Brothers Osborne for a rendition of their hit collaboration \u201cBurning Man.\u201d The single appears on Bentley\u2019s upcoming ninth studio album, The Mountain, which will drop Friday.\n\nJeff Kravitz/FilmMagic\n\nBe sure to check out PEOPLE\u2019s full CMT Awards coverage to get the latest news on country\u2019s big night.\n\nThe Music City mainstay married his wife, Cassidy, in 2005, and the pair share three children: daughters Evelyn, 9, and Jordan, 7, and their 4-year-old son Knox.\n\nRELATED VIDEO: Dierks Bentley Launches Clothing Line With Flag & Anthem\n\nBentley previously opened up to PEOPLE about how his life as a performer has changed as his family expanded.\n\n\u201cHangovers last longer than they used to,\u201d he quipped in a 2016 interview, also revealing he brings his brood on the road when he tours. \u201cWe\u2019ll grab a second bus and come out, and I\u2019ll load that bus with kiddie pools and remote control cars and chalk and water balloons and rockets to shoot up in the air \u2014 everything.\u201d\n\nThe 2018 CMT Music Awards are broadcast live from Nashville on Wednesday, June 6 at 8 p.m. ET/PT on CMT.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/acwXKQakAZoSzmxzquUi3-5YI8g=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(715x0:717x2)/dierks-bentley-b45a08811f5a42fe8daf3a4c4a36f851.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/EF23RHk_U-GNMjXg0fOsnl110Xc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(959x439:961x441)/leslie-jordan-tribute-01-022123-0319388b1f79435c98faf678abd788b2.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/E-LhNkE6YMtJnxvMYT8tEuinB-I=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(644x19:646x21)/megan-moroney-album-lucky-050423-7-dd353c88d4d5411483b5e35d29b862ce.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/sb5XDzcNqklkyi1i6MI-FZ0GIQU=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/acm-noms-041323-1-0de025906db346eba8ad3f01f29b36b6.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/doQ4rVAEQ2mK9k7mei5-KwnYoNc=/75x75/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Jeff-Nelson_selects-10-85889a30a8544ebba85c86033bc5b46a.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/N65NE--M4btFjK2hQwLzXw2v95M=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(794x359:796x361)/CMT-Awards-Blake-Shelton-and-Gwen-Stefani-01-2023-2c28358bba8f434c9920b2de31d4f619.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/bJ9zZZHuSKbOwPK5A93NDxlxzc8=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(701x0:703x2)/dierks-bentley-1-f0503f4404204cb0b6d64546c0dec40b.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/K3jrXymYj84eVJXPlbmN7wkQomw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/dolly-garth-acm-split-091023-0bd7dedf7ade4e83b2a4cbab8114df8b.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/VWCwkIMTeBFJk78CnvbBb-Ntl1k=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/carly-pearce-trisha-yearwood-cole-swindell-jo-dee-messina-split-tout-050923-2014c9a33ed24fc2b2aae82a3b6b47c6.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Lje7sGaj3HgeS-yLg9z5JSNPfrU=/300x150/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/people_magazine_sub-e6689738996d40f38f154099e1751481.png", "https://people.com/thmb/mj28wJF_nWMWUrdKY7pzF8s2tvw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/scotty-McCreery-CMT-Stage-050323-2-393b84399ef14